Psionic_Blast.help: You fire a psionic burst at the target, causing psionic damage and reducing attack speed.
Psionic_Blast.targetHelp: Your attack speed has been reduced.

Psionic_Torment.help: You create painful visions within the mind of your target, causing psionic damage. These visions manifest as wounds that cause lethal damage over time. Affected targets also suffer reduced regeneration, recovery and attack speed.
Psionic_Torment.targetHelp: You are suffering lethal damage over time. Additionally, your regeneration, recovery and attack speed have been reduced.

Psionic_Crush.help: You imprison your target in a field of collapsing psionic energy. They are held in place and suffer continuous psionic damage and endurance loss.
Psionic_Crush.shortHelp: Ranged, Minor DMG (Psionic), Moderate DoT (Psionic), -End (Foe), Hold (Foe)
Psionic_Crush.targetHelp: You are suffering psionic damage over time and losing endurance.

Psionic_Shock.targetHelp: You are losing endurance over time.

Psionic_Pulse.help: You unleash a powerful psionic shockwave that ripples through the air around you, dealing Psionic and Smashing damage to any hit by the wave. The shockwave also has a chance to knockback its targets.
Psionic_Pulse.shortHelp: PBAoE, Moderate DMG (Psionic/Smashing), Chance for Knockback (Foe)

Psionic_Void.help: You create a field of psionic energy at the feet of up to two targets. This field deals continuous psionic damage over time.

Psionic_Flow.help: You create a powerful stream of psionic energy. This causes significant psionic damage to all enemies caught in its field, as well as drains endurance and lowers recovery.
Psionic_Flow.shortHelp: Ranged (Targeted AoE), Extreme DMG (Psionic), -End (Foe), -Rec (Foe), +DMG(Self, Psionic), +DEF(Self, Psionic)
Psionic_Flow.targetHelp: You are losing endurance over time and your recovery has been reduced.
